# Cleaning Log

## Cleaning Philosophy

The project follows a validation-first and data-integrity-first approach.

Validation activities were completed before any cleaning actions were considered.

Where business rules were unavailable, original dataset values were retained to avoid unsupported assumptions.

The raw dataset will remain unchanged throughout the project.

---

## Cleaning Session 1



Objective:

Perform initial data-cleaning review focused on formatting consistency, field standardization, and structural assessment.

No records will be deleted during this stage.

No placeholder values will be modified without documented justification.

