## Geographic Review

Seller geographic fields were reviewed for consistency.

Findings included:

- State abbreviations and full state names (TX/Texas, FL/Florida, CA/California)
- Multiple representations of United States in Seller Country
- Capitalization inconsistencies within Seller City values

Cleaning Actions Performed:

- City Of Industry → City of Industry
- Multiple locations → Multiple Locations

No changes were made to state or country values.

Reason:

Business rules and geographic reference documentation were unavailable. Source-system values were retained to preserve data integrity and maintain traceability.

No modification has been performed at this stage.
